-And then from 10--
      -Armando.

31
00:01:24,718 --> 00:01:26,585
Do you have
              any time scheduled

32
00:01:26,587 --> 00:01:27,753
for me
               to take a breath?

33
00:01:27,755 --> 00:01:29,088
Breath, breath, breath.

34
00:01:29,090 --> 00:01:31,423
Nope. But I can pencil it in.

35
00:01:31,425 --> 00:01:32,691
Ugh! How am I
                 supposed to get

36
00:01:32,693 --> 00:01:34,726
through
       this entire scroll today?

37
00:01:34,728 --> 00:01:35,727
[scroll tears]

38
00:01:35,729 --> 00:01:38,230
Well, there's one way.

39
00:01:38,232 --> 00:01:39,865
I'm sorry, Princess,

40
00:01:39,867 --> 00:01:42,101
but now that
Chancellor Esteban is gone--

41
