to arrive until this afternoon.

176
00:07:11,198 --> 00:07:13,698
Should I tell them
      to come back later?

177
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:15,600
What? No. Uh...

178
00:07:15,602 --> 00:07:18,136
Show them the Hydro-Gondola
we built on the terrace,

179
00:07:18,138 --> 00:07:20,071
