I'm back!

230
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:31,503
What happened?

231
00:09:31,505 --> 00:09:33,905
The Carizans showed up
          early for a meeting,

232
00:09:33,907 --> 00:09:36,274
and they're waiting for us
      to get back to the palace.

233
00:09:36,276 --> 00:09:39,544
-Gotta run!
        -But what about
        our chocolates?

234
00:09:39,546 --> 00:09:42,347
Well, we already made
           a whole day's worth.

235
00:09:42,349 --> 00:09:43,848
So quickly?

236
